cat << EOF
GNU Mailutils contains a series of useful mail clients, servers, and libraries.
These are the primary mail utilities of the GNU system. Specifically, this 
package contains a POP3 server, an IMAP4 server, and a Sieve mail filter. It 
also provides a POSIX 'mailx' client and a collection of other tools.
EOF
